result.name: Hui Lau Shan

reviews.text: Ordered the dessert with the taro but no taro was served. Got 3 tiny pieces of mango (which was tasty no doubt), 3 tiny pieces of glass jelly, a bunch of the pumpkin/sweet potato balls which were hard and a bunch of the chewy balls which were tasteless and stuck to the teeth. Standard has dropped for sure, perhaps it’s on a franchise model?
Great if you like mango, but not so great if you prefer dairy desserts.
Food dessert place, but losing it's uniqueness. More and more mango desserts are popping up and tasting better than these guys. Go here for convenience.
The food here is delicious.
They make amazing mango mochi!

result.name: 許留山

reviews.text: 흔히 예상할 수 있는 망고주스와 망고 빙수의 맛으로 잠실에도 허유산이 있으니 굳이 방문할 필요가 있나 싶다. 더운 홍콩 거리를 다니다가 보이면 들어가서 시원한 빙수와 주스를 먹을만하지만, 굳이 찾아갈 필요는 없을 듯하다.

マンゴープリンとか、見た目はキッチュなんですけど、
食べたら「ああ香港に来たなぁ」ってうれしくなります。
店が狭くて、すぐ満席になるのが難点ですが、
多店舗展開しているので、いろんなところで気軽に利用できるのがいいですね。

Ordered the dessert with the taro but no taro was served. Got 3 tiny pieces of mango (which was tasty no doubt), 3 tiny pieces of glass jelly, a bunch of the pumpkin/sweet potato balls which were hard and a bunch of the chewy balls which were tasteless and stuck to the teeth. Standard has dropped for sure, perhaps it’s on a franchise model?
坦白講，D質素每況愈下
Great if you like mango, but not so great if you prefer dairy desserts.
